---
title: Turmeric-Roasted Cauliflower Bowl with Couscous & Spiced Tomato Sauce
description: We love the tender texture of couscous, each fluffy grain holds its shape and easily soaks up bold flavours (in this case, a spiced tomato sauce!). Combine that with spiced roasted veggies, a yoghurt drizzle and a smattering of roasted cashews and this is a bowl to remember!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/turmeric-roasted-cauliflower-bowl-823275b8.jpg
